59
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:10,800
"Love Sea The Home for Lovers"
(Episode 6)

60
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,810
Big brother is so cruel, abandoning me.

61
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,400
You heartless guy

62
